come rain , come shine ( hangul : 사랑한다 , 사랑하지 않는다 ; rr : saranghanda , saranghaji anneunda ; literally " i love you , i love you not " ) is a 2011 south korean film by lee yoon-ki . a young woman ( im soo-jung ) informs her husband of five years ( hyun bin ) that she is leaving him for another man ( ha jung-woo ) , but the husband remains calm and even helps her pack . the experimental film traces in real-time parts of their last three hours together while the wife prepares to move out . the film premiered in competition at the 61st berlin international film festival in 2011 .